@startuml
title BP-14 - Allowed Payment Method Configuration

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|School Administrator|
start
:Open school payment method settings;
:Select allowed methods;
:Configure method specific information;

|Platform|
:Validate tenant scope;
:Validate payment method support;
:Validate required provider credentials if needed;

if (Configuration valid?) then (Yes)
  :Save allowed payment method settings;
else (No)
  :Return validation error;
  stop
endif

|Parent Guardian|
:See only methods allowed by the school;

|Finance Officer|
:Use cash method if manual collection is allowed;
stop

note right
Current PaymentOrder supports:
CASH, BANK_TRANSFER, VIRTUAL_ACCOUNT, QRIS, CREDIT_CARD.
External provider configuration is future scope.
end note
@enduml
